        "question": "<p style=\"orphans:2;widows:2\"> <span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><b>Consider the following statements about the Trinity of Carnatic Music and choose the correct option:</b></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"orphans:2;widows:2\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><b>Statement 1: Tyagaraja, Muthuswami Dikshitar, and Shyama Shastri lived during the 17th century.</b></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"orphans:2;widows:2\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none\"><b>Statement 2: The trinity elevated the kriti form to its highest artistic expression.</b></span></span></span></span></p>",
